<DATELINE>ELIZABETH, N.J. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Mary Matlosz of Fourth Avenue won $2 in
the New Jersey Lottery but no share of April 15th's $69.9 million
Illinois Lotto jackpot. That was Mary Matlosz of Maple Avenue.
   Nonetheless, people have been calling the wrong Mrs. Matlosz to
