<FILEID>AP-NR-04-26-89 1226EST</FILEID>
<FIRST>r i BC-Soviet-Promotions     04-26 0337</FIRST>
<SECOND>BC-Soviet-Promotions,0361</SECOND>
<HEAD>Names of Central Committee Candidates Elevated to Full Membership</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The 24 candidate Central Committee members
elevated to full membership, as provided by the official Tass news
agency:
   _ Veniamin G. Afonin, first secretary of the Kuibyshev regional
party committee.
   _ Alexander A. Babenko, deputy chairman of the Council of
Ministers of the Russian Republic.
   _ Yevgeny P. Velikhov, vice president of the Academy of Sciences.
   _ Vladimir. V. Grigoriev, first secretary of the Vitebsk
regional party committee.
